<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM2.7.11">
<l>paṟpa nāpa ṉuyarvaṟa vuyarum peruntiṟalō</l>
<l>ṉeṟpara ṉeṉṉai yākkikkoṇ ṭeṉakkē taṉṉaittanta</l>
<l>kaṟpaka meṉṉamutaṅ kārmukil pōlum vēṅkaṭanal</l>
<l>veṟpaṉ vicumpōr pirāṉentai tāmō taraṉē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>He in whose navel is a lotus, the powerful one who is high beyond height,</l>
<l>my Highest one, wishfulfilling tree who made me for himself [and] gave himself</l> 
<l>just to me, my ambrosia, the man from the good mountain of Vēṅkaṭam</l>
<l>who resembles a rain cloud, the lord of the celestials, [is] our father, Tamōtaraṉ.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
